1
00:01:38,165 --> 00:01:40,801
If you're here to taunt me,
please go away.

2
00:01:52,946 --> 00:01:54,047
I'm sorry.

3
00:01:54,681 --> 00:01:56,249
I was out of line before.

4
00:01:57,551 --> 00:01:58,885
Because the women around me

5
00:01:59,386 --> 00:02:00,721
are all frivolous and easy.

6
00:02:01,989 --> 00:02:02,990
So...

7
00:02:15,736 --> 00:02:18,205
There are many things I don't
care about in this world.

8
00:02:19,373 --> 00:02:22,275
I don't care about relationships,

9
00:02:22,609 --> 00:02:24,044
including family and love.

10
00:02:25,045 --> 00:02:26,446
However, I realized I've changed lately.

11
00:02:27,948 --> 00:02:29,082
I became happy.

12
00:02:30,317 --> 00:02:31,618
I'm happy every day.

13
00:02:38,191 --> 00:02:40,160
I think it started after I met you.

14
00:02:46,266 --> 00:02:47,668
Please don't touch me again.

15
00:02:48,402 --> 00:02:49,903
I don't feel that way about you.

16
00:02:51,605 --> 00:02:53,306
Okay, I promise you,

17
00:02:53,774 --> 00:02:55,175
we'll do it your way.

18
00:03:00,947 --> 00:03:01,948
Are you busy later?

19
00:03:03,817 --> 00:03:04,985
I'm going to work.

20
00:03:07,654 --> 00:03:08,588
I'll take you there.

21
00:03:18,331 --> 00:03:19,166
Shancai.

22
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:21,501
Qinghe.

23
00:03:23,103 --> 00:03:24,137
-Who is he?
-Oh.

24
00:03:24,204 --> 00:03:25,972
He's Yamen. This is Qinghe.

25
00:03:26,039 --> 00:03:26,973
Hi.

26
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:27,974
Yamen?

27
00:03:28,608 --> 00:03:30,177
Where are you going?

28
00:03:30,510 --> 00:03:31,545
I'm going to work.

29
00:03:31,611 --> 00:03:32,846
I'm taking her there.

30
00:03:35,749 --> 00:03:36,650
Qinghe?

31
00:03:37,584 --> 00:03:38,618
Nothing.

32
00:03:38,685 --> 00:03:41,354
-I'll get going then. Bye-bye.
-Bye-bye.

33
00:03:45,325 --> 00:03:46,860
What's going on?

34
00:03:47,260 --> 00:03:49,362
Why is Shancai
with Daoming Si's fake cousin?

35
00:03:53,500 --> 00:03:54,601
Daoming Si.

36
00:03:57,704 --> 00:03:58,605
What's up?

37
00:03:59,239 --> 00:04:00,173
Well...

38
00:04:01,341 --> 00:04:02,175
Well...

39
00:04:02,642 --> 00:04:03,477
What?

40
00:04:05,612 --> 00:04:07,047
I don't know how to say this.

41
00:04:07,514 --> 00:04:08,615
Just say it.

42
00:04:15,122 --> 00:04:16,223
What a nice day.

43
00:04:16,757 --> 00:04:18,992
I really like to wander the streets
on days like this.

44
00:04:20,427 --> 00:04:23,230
Didn't I tell you to stop daydreaming?
Why are you still daydreaming?

45
00:04:25,732 --> 00:04:27,334
How about you skip work this afternoon?

46
00:04:28,001 --> 00:04:28,869
Let's hang out.

47
00:04:31,671 --> 00:04:33,907
Can we go somewhere
that doesn't require a lot of thinking?

48
00:04:35,008 --> 00:04:36,109
Let's go to the amusement park.

49
00:04:37,344 --> 00:04:39,679
Amusement park? Great.

50
00:04:39,746 --> 00:04:41,181
Can I ride the roller coaster?

51
00:04:41,648 --> 00:04:43,850
Yes. But I won't ride with you.

52
00:04:43,917 --> 00:04:45,218
Are you scared?

53
00:04:48,989 --> 00:04:51,224
I started thinking
you're actually pretty nice lately.

54
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:56,263
I don't know.
I tried to lie to you before.

55
00:04:58,265 --> 00:05:00,300
But you told me the truth.

56
00:05:00,734 --> 00:05:02,836
It's better than lying
to me until the end.

57
00:05:04,237 --> 00:05:07,340
So... can I touch you?

58
00:05:07,707 --> 00:05:10,377
Of course you can't.
Those are two different things, okay?

59
00:05:10,443 --> 00:05:12,379
Don't be so serious. I'm just joking.

60
00:05:15,448 --> 00:05:18,185
If we want to go to the amusement park,
which bus should we take?

61
00:05:18,785 --> 00:05:21,555
I don't know either.
I haven't taken a bus for 15 years.

62
00:05:21,621 --> 00:05:24,291
It's been 15 years? I recently...

63
00:05:24,791 --> 00:05:28,261
This is our first date today.
Be happy, put a smile on your face.

64
00:05:29,429 --> 00:05:31,164
You're so handsome.

65
00:05:31,698 --> 00:05:32,732
What happened recently?

66
00:05:34,601 --> 00:05:36,803
I've always wanted to go
to the amusement park recently.

67
00:05:39,439 --> 00:05:45,445
<i>I can only hope, that the pain in my heart
will fade away one day.</i>

68
00:05:47,414 --> 00:05:50,383
Okay, I know which bus we should take.
Let's go.

69
00:05:56,356 --> 00:05:57,457
Daoming Si.

70
00:05:58,525 --> 00:05:59,459
Shancai.

71
00:06:00,126 --> 00:06:00,961
Don't go.

72
00:06:01,695 --> 00:06:02,796
Don't go with him.

73
00:06:02,863 --> 00:06:03,997
What are you talking about?

74
00:06:09,469 --> 00:06:10,470
I can't live without you.

75
00:06:12,472 --> 00:06:13,540
I can't lose you.

76
00:06:17,677 --> 00:06:18,578
Without you,

77
00:06:20,046 --> 00:06:21,882
I don't what will happen to my life.

78
00:06:23,984 --> 00:06:25,952
I wouldn't be able
to live like a normal person.

79
00:06:28,221 --> 00:06:29,890
I really have no idea what I would do

80
00:06:31,191 --> 00:06:32,158
if I lose you.

81
00:06:34,294 --> 00:06:36,463
You're not a kid anymore.
Don't be so naive, okay?

82
00:06:36,963 --> 00:06:38,965
You're putting Shancai
in a difficult situation right now.

83
00:06:39,032 --> 00:06:41,601
Right, I am a kid.

84
00:06:43,270 --> 00:06:45,105
I used to do whatever I want to do.

85
00:06:46,673 --> 00:06:48,575
Now I really don't know what
to do anymore.

86
00:06:49,843 --> 00:06:50,977
Shancai, tell me.

87
00:06:51,444 --> 00:06:54,948
What should I do to be able to love you?

88
00:06:56,683 --> 00:06:57,584
That's enough.

89
00:06:59,019 --> 00:07:00,820
Have you ever thought about her happiness?

90
00:07:02,255 --> 00:07:04,591
If you've ever thought for her
from her perspective,

91
00:07:05,292 --> 00:07:07,027
you'll give her a peaceful life.

92
00:07:08,328 --> 00:07:09,796
That is love.

93
00:07:10,797 --> 00:07:13,767
Happiness? I want happiness, too.

94
00:07:14,801 --> 00:07:17,103
Shancai, listen to me.

95
00:07:18,071 --> 00:07:20,774
No matter what happens,
I'll protect you with my life.

96
00:07:21,241 --> 00:07:22,309
You have to believe me.

97
00:07:30,784 --> 00:07:32,185
Are you going to get on the bus?

98
00:07:32,252 --> 00:07:33,586
Yes, wait a minute.

99
00:07:36,923 --> 00:07:38,625
This is the most painful moment.

100
00:07:39,192 --> 00:07:41,061
You'll get your relief after this.

101
00:07:41,394 --> 00:07:44,197
Don't act on emotions.
It's bad for both of you.

102
00:08:05,185 --> 00:08:06,252
Shancai.

103
00:08:09,556 --> 00:08:12,192
Shancai!

104
00:08:14,427 --> 00:08:15,428
Shancai!

105
00:08:18,598 --> 00:08:19,632
Shancai!

106
00:08:22,402 --> 00:08:23,403
Shancai!

107
00:08:24,938 --> 00:08:25,872
Shancai!

108
00:09:14,220 --> 00:09:15,588
Stop the bus.

109
00:09:15,655 --> 00:09:17,190
Sorry, Miss, I can't stop here.

110
00:09:17,257 --> 00:09:19,526
-Please, let me get off the bus.
-No, not here.

111
00:09:19,592 --> 00:09:21,428
I'm begging you,
I have to get off the bus now.

112
00:09:21,494 --> 00:09:22,929
Fine, I'll park the bus aside.

113
00:09:30,603 --> 00:09:31,938
Won't you regret this?

114
00:09:33,706 --> 00:09:35,708
I don't know if love is real.

115
00:09:36,409 --> 00:09:39,846
I don't know that.
So I'm going to find the answer myself.

116
00:09:52,559 --> 00:09:53,560
Are we good to go?

117
00:09:54,894 --> 00:09:56,396
Please drive, thanks.

118
00:10:21,187 --> 00:10:22,922
<i>I have no time to think.</i>

119
00:10:22,989 --> 00:10:25,925
<i>No matter what the consequences
of my actions will bring,</i>

120
00:10:26,759 --> 00:10:30,196
<i>whether I'll regret it or not,
all I want to do is run to him.</i>

121
00:10:30,730 --> 00:10:34,734
<i>At this moment, my body
and soul are connected together.</i>

122
00:10:38,104 --> 00:10:41,107
Idiot. Do you know it's dangerous
to sit there?

123
00:10:55,755 --> 00:10:59,058
<i>I don't want to lie anymore.
I've crossed that bridge.</i>

124
00:11:14,007 --> 00:11:15,375
<i>Lei called me yesterday.</i>

125
00:11:15,708 --> 00:11:17,710
Really? What did he say?

126
00:11:18,178 --> 00:11:19,112
He said he's been busy.

127
00:11:19,512 --> 00:11:22,215
But he's worried how things are going on
between Shancai and Ah Si.

128
00:11:25,151 --> 00:11:26,519
How do you think things are going now?

129
00:11:27,754 --> 00:11:28,855
How else could it be?

130
00:11:29,389 --> 00:11:31,124
I think Lei doesn't have to worry now.

131
00:11:32,292 --> 00:11:34,093
F4 minus one. You're here.

132
00:11:34,160 --> 00:11:37,030
F4 minus one? Are you looking for trouble?

133
00:11:37,096 --> 00:11:38,097
I'm telling the truth.

134
00:11:38,164 --> 00:11:40,600
Daoming Si asked me to join F4 before
but you two wouldn't allow it.

135
00:11:40,667 --> 00:11:43,503
-It's not that we wouldn't allow it.
-Meizuo, you're the best.

136
00:11:44,470 --> 00:11:47,574
I haven't finished yet.
We would rather die than allow it.

137
00:11:48,274 --> 00:11:49,475
I don't care.

138
00:11:50,310 --> 00:11:52,845
Daoming Si, did you find that fake cousin?

139
00:11:53,179 --> 00:11:54,814
Shut up, okay?

140
00:11:55,348 --> 00:11:56,883
Why are you so mad?

141
00:11:57,250 --> 00:11:58,918
Did Shancai stop talking
to you again yesterday?

142
00:11:58,985 --> 00:12:00,353
Keep talking and I'll beat you up.

143
00:12:02,121 --> 00:12:03,656
So that fake cousin won in the end.

144
00:12:03,723 --> 00:12:04,958
Do you want to get beaten up?

145
00:12:06,192 --> 00:12:07,694
Are you and Shancai okay now or what?

146
00:12:08,127 --> 00:12:09,362
Lei's worried about you.

147
00:12:12,332 --> 00:12:13,166
Hello.

148
00:12:14,834 --> 00:12:16,869
Oh, I know.

149
00:12:17,437 --> 00:12:18,905
I have things to attend to. I'm leaving.

150
00:12:18,972 --> 00:12:21,007
Hey, Ah Si, where are you going?
You haven't finished yet.

151
00:12:21,674 --> 00:12:23,076
I don't think there's any need for that.

152
00:12:27,780 --> 00:12:29,415
Your family
owns Qingchi Corporation, right?

153
00:12:30,250 --> 00:12:31,484
Yeah, that's right.

154
00:12:32,919 --> 00:12:35,855
Judging by Ah Si and the others,
we should be more careful.

155
00:12:36,256 --> 00:12:37,991
-Yeah.
-What do you mean? I don't understand.

156
00:12:38,992 --> 00:12:40,827
Shut up. I'll tell you if need to know.

157
00:12:51,904 --> 00:12:52,739
Shancai.

158
00:12:54,774 --> 00:12:56,376
What are you doing?

159
00:13:00,813 --> 00:13:02,482
It's not my stomach rumbling.

160
00:13:03,116 --> 00:13:04,217
It's not mine either.

161
00:13:04,717 --> 00:13:06,753
Why don't you just admit
that you're hungry?

162
00:13:06,819 --> 00:13:08,388
Why do you keep nitpicking?

163
00:13:08,454 --> 00:13:11,391
I'm telling the truth. It's not like
I'm the one who always hungry.

164
00:13:12,825 --> 00:13:14,360
You're so cute when you act like this.

165
00:13:15,461 --> 00:13:18,298
What are you talking about?
I don't know what you're thinking about.

166
00:13:18,364 --> 00:13:20,333
I'm the one who wants
to know what you're thinking about.

167
00:13:21,601 --> 00:13:24,137
You must be thinking

168
00:13:25,471 --> 00:13:26,873
about me, right?

169
00:13:28,741 --> 00:13:29,642
Idiot.

170
00:13:30,777 --> 00:13:33,413
Yeah, I shouldn't be talking like that.

171
00:13:38,017 --> 00:13:39,085
You have a passport, right?

172
00:13:39,619 --> 00:13:40,720
Passport?

173
00:13:40,787 --> 00:13:43,489
Didn't you get one for me last time
when we went to Liuqiu?

174
00:13:44,991 --> 00:13:46,993
Right. I want to take you to New York.

175
00:13:47,660 --> 00:13:48,494
What?

176
00:13:48,561 --> 00:13:51,597
Are you talking about
that shopping mall New York New York?

177
00:13:55,468 --> 00:13:57,270
I want to make a plan in advance.

178
00:13:58,171 --> 00:13:59,339
What plan?

179
00:13:59,405 --> 00:14:01,841
-I want to take you straight to--
-Wait. Don't rush.

180
00:14:01,908 --> 00:14:03,176
I don't think it's a good idea.

181
00:14:03,910 --> 00:14:04,777
Why?

182
00:14:05,678 --> 00:14:06,779
Because I don't want to do it.

183
00:14:08,214 --> 00:14:09,248
You don't want to do it?

184
00:14:10,850 --> 00:14:13,553
Because we have to go to school.
And New York is so far.

185
00:14:13,619 --> 00:14:15,288
And my English sucks.

186
00:14:15,355 --> 00:14:16,956
Don't avoid my question.

187
00:14:17,023 --> 00:14:19,692
I'm asking you.
Why did you get off the bus that day?

188
00:14:20,993 --> 00:14:22,395
Am I having the wrong idea again?

189
00:14:22,995 --> 00:14:24,163
What are you talking about?

190
00:14:25,198 --> 00:14:26,366
Why did you get off the bus?

191
00:14:28,067 --> 00:14:29,068
Why?

192
00:14:30,069 --> 00:14:30,903
Because...

193
00:14:32,805 --> 00:14:35,541
<i>Is this guy making me confess my love
to him?</i>

194
00:14:37,610 --> 00:14:38,444
<i>Xiaoyou.</i>

195
00:14:38,811 --> 00:14:40,413
-Here's the last one.
-Okay.

196
00:14:45,485 --> 00:14:48,388
Shancai isn't here today,
so your workload is heavier than usual.

197
00:14:48,454 --> 00:14:49,589
I'm so sorry.

198
00:14:50,022 --> 00:14:51,758
Boss, that's okay.

199
00:14:51,824 --> 00:14:54,660
The economy is weak now
and there is less business here.

200
00:14:55,395 --> 00:14:59,232
It's not just here.
Everyone is having a hard time now.

201
00:15:00,466 --> 00:15:01,467
Welcome.

202
00:15:01,934 --> 00:15:03,436
-Ximen.
-Hi.

203
00:15:03,770 --> 00:15:06,506
Aren't you the one
who helped us last time?

204
00:15:06,973 --> 00:15:09,108
-Sorry for the hassle last time.
-Not at all.

205
00:15:10,476 --> 00:15:11,911
Could I borrow her for a while?

206
00:15:11,978 --> 00:15:14,080
But I don't have enough hands here
right now.

207
00:15:14,614 --> 00:15:15,615
I see.

208
00:15:17,383 --> 00:15:18,284
How about this?

209
00:15:18,651 --> 00:15:22,021
I'll buy all the cakes
and desserts you baked today.

210
00:15:22,388 --> 00:15:24,724
What? You're going to buy all of them?

211
00:15:25,558 --> 00:15:27,226
There's a tea party at my place tomorrow.

212
00:15:28,761 --> 00:15:30,096
Okay, thank you.

213
00:15:31,431 --> 00:15:32,565
Are you free now?

214
00:15:35,735 --> 00:15:39,572
<i>It's so hard to say the words
that are deeply hidden in my heart.</i>

215
00:15:40,506 --> 00:15:43,576
<i>But I have to make today a real start.</i>

216
00:15:45,044 --> 00:15:47,413
<i>I have to say "I love you" out loud.</i>

217
00:15:48,848 --> 00:15:50,383
<i>Or else we won't get started.</i>

218
00:15:56,956 --> 00:15:58,891
Well...

219
00:15:58,958 --> 00:16:01,327
Well, what? Say it.

220
00:16:02,228 --> 00:16:04,063
I'm too scared to say it if you're so mad.

221
00:16:04,597 --> 00:16:05,731
What do you mean?

222
00:16:06,299 --> 00:16:07,366
Say it now.

223
00:16:09,335 --> 00:16:12,104
I'm so hungry. Are you hungry?
Do you want to eat bento?

224
00:16:14,173 --> 00:16:17,109
I made it myself.
You haven't had lunch, right?

225
00:16:17,176 --> 00:16:19,111
But they're just normal dishes.

226
00:16:20,012 --> 00:16:22,315
-You made it for me?
-Yeah.

227
00:16:22,648 --> 00:16:24,750
But I don't know if you'll like it.

228
00:16:25,084 --> 00:16:26,085
I want to eat it.

229
00:16:39,932 --> 00:16:42,235
What? Is this thing like a jellyfish?

230
00:16:42,301 --> 00:16:45,004
Jellyfish? That's a mini sausage.

231
00:16:46,172 --> 00:16:47,106
Mini...

232
00:16:52,879 --> 00:16:53,880
How is it?

233
00:16:56,315 --> 00:16:57,750
It has its unique flavor.

234
00:16:58,551 --> 00:16:59,785
Unique?

235
00:17:00,486 --> 00:17:02,488
You don' have to eat it
if you don't like it.

236
00:17:02,555 --> 00:17:03,623
Young Masters like you

237
00:17:03,689 --> 00:17:06,526
must be eating dishes prepared
by master chefs every day, right?

238
00:17:06,592 --> 00:17:08,194
Of course, you won't like
these simple dishes.

239
00:17:10,696 --> 00:17:13,232
Wasn't there any other girl who prepared
a bento for you before?

240
00:17:14,166 --> 00:17:16,969
There was but I thought they
were terrifying so I didn't eat them.

241
00:17:17,570 --> 00:17:20,540
Then why are you eating this now?

242
00:17:27,413 --> 00:17:29,515
I thought you would start over
with Xiaozi.

243
00:17:30,483 --> 00:17:31,384
Xiaozi?

244
00:17:33,519 --> 00:17:35,855
I saw you two sitting in a cafe that day.

245
00:17:37,056 --> 00:17:38,925
How could I be sitting
with someone I don't love?

246
00:17:39,492 --> 00:17:40,660
You don't know me at all.

247
00:17:41,160 --> 00:17:42,662
Then will you be my boyfriend?

248
00:17:43,696 --> 00:17:44,964
Hey, are you okay?

249
00:17:46,766 --> 00:17:49,068
Why are you saying that like it's nothing?

250
00:17:49,135 --> 00:17:50,570
For real?

251
00:17:51,404 --> 00:17:52,872
-Come here.
-What?

252
00:17:52,939 --> 00:17:55,374
Just hide. Your feet.

253
00:17:55,441 --> 00:17:57,043
-For real?
-Yeah.

254
00:17:57,777 --> 00:17:59,078
Hey, look.

255
00:17:59,979 --> 00:18:01,247
There aren't many people here.

256
00:18:01,647 --> 00:18:03,115
We won't be spotted.

257
00:18:03,649 --> 00:18:06,085
-Really? How do you know that?
-Yeah.

258
00:18:06,619 --> 00:18:08,387
I just wanted to be
with you without anyone else,

259
00:18:08,454 --> 00:18:10,089
so I checked this place before.

260
00:18:10,156 --> 00:18:12,024
Really?

261
00:18:12,792 --> 00:18:15,194
Hey, don't do it.
What if someone comes here?

262
00:18:15,261 --> 00:18:17,863
What's the problem?
We'll make out in front of them.

263
00:18:18,831 --> 00:18:21,000
We can't. Someone will come here.

264
00:18:22,134 --> 00:18:24,003
I haven't finished what I was saying.

265
00:18:24,637 --> 00:18:26,505
I hope we can keep it confidential.

266
00:18:28,140 --> 00:18:29,141
Keep what confidential?

267
00:18:29,542 --> 00:18:31,210
Our relationship.

268
00:18:32,411 --> 00:18:34,347
You want us to be
in a secret relationship?

269
00:18:34,714 --> 00:18:38,050
No. I mean, we won't keep it
that way forever.

270
00:18:38,117 --> 00:18:41,721
Could we keep it confidential
before someone finds out?

271
00:18:42,121 --> 00:18:43,389
Are you kidding me?

272
00:18:46,325 --> 00:18:48,127
Don't disturb me here! Get out of my face!

273
00:18:48,194 --> 00:18:50,496
-Sorry. We didn't know you're here.
-Get lost!

274
00:18:51,897 --> 00:18:52,932
Are you mad?

275
00:18:55,001 --> 00:18:57,136
Of course, I'm mad!

276
00:18:57,703 --> 00:18:59,105
A secret relationship.

277
00:18:59,872 --> 00:19:01,674
Why? Are you embarrassed of me?

278
00:19:05,211 --> 00:19:07,680
<i>No, we'll be doomed in the end.</i>

279
00:19:08,047 --> 00:19:10,816
<i>Everything will happen all over again.
I can't give up.</i>

280
00:19:12,318 --> 00:19:13,686
Daoming Si, listen to me.

281
00:19:16,288 --> 00:19:17,556
I want to be with you.

282
00:19:19,091 --> 00:19:20,960
But if your mom finds out,

283
00:19:22,161 --> 00:19:24,063
she will try to sabotage
our relationship again, right?

284
00:19:25,931 --> 00:19:26,866
I don't...

285
00:19:28,567 --> 00:19:30,803
I don't want to break up
with you like the last time.

286
00:19:32,271 --> 00:19:33,272
I've had enough.

287
00:19:35,441 --> 00:19:36,742
On that rainy night,

288
00:19:37,610 --> 00:19:38,878
my heart was broken.

289
00:19:40,279 --> 00:19:42,314
I don't want
to go through that pain again.

290
00:19:49,889 --> 00:19:50,956
I've made up my mind.

291
00:19:51,957 --> 00:19:53,359
I will do whatever I have to do.

292
00:19:54,126 --> 00:19:56,462
For you, I will even go against my mom.

293
00:19:58,364 --> 00:19:59,265
Idiot.

294
00:20:00,066 --> 00:20:01,500
I'm not telling you to do that.

295
00:20:03,335 --> 00:20:04,937
I'm just really scared.

296
00:20:06,305 --> 00:20:09,075
Maybe on our way to New York,

297
00:20:09,442 --> 00:20:11,577
Xiaoyou and Qinghe's families
will be ruined.

298
00:20:13,145 --> 00:20:14,980
I really want to be with you,

299
00:20:16,015 --> 00:20:19,418
but I can't leave them behind.

300
00:20:26,492 --> 00:20:27,326
Fine.

301
00:20:28,894 --> 00:20:30,596
Let's keep our relationship as a secret
for now.

302
00:20:32,098 --> 00:20:34,467
But I'm telling you,
we can't hide it for long.

303
00:20:36,402 --> 00:20:37,570
We'll see when the time comes.

304
00:20:38,771 --> 00:20:41,207
Okay. Thank you, Daoming Si.

305
00:20:42,007 --> 00:20:45,044
Wait, what are you doing?
What if people find out?

306
00:20:45,111 --> 00:20:47,213
We're in a relationship now
and you're still holding it back?

307
00:20:47,279 --> 00:20:48,147
I'm not.

308
00:20:48,647 --> 00:20:49,949
What's wrong with a kiss?

309
00:20:50,382 --> 00:20:51,317
No.

310
00:20:51,951 --> 00:20:54,120
My heart is pounding so fast now.

311
00:20:54,553 --> 00:20:55,654
Another day, okay?

312
00:20:58,190 --> 00:20:59,391
Am I too bossy?

313
00:21:00,025 --> 00:21:01,060
Of course, you're bossy.

314
00:21:01,127 --> 00:21:03,062
If you have a tea party at your place,

315
00:21:03,129 --> 00:21:06,432
